fields.question: ❓Q: How do I place an order?
fields.answer: A: Simply browse the products, add items to your cart, and proceed to checkout. You can choose to pay online or opt for Cash on Delivery.

fields.question: ❓Q: Can I return or cancel a product after ordering?
fields.answer: A: Yes, you can cancel orders before they are shipped. If your product is delivered, you can initiate a return request from your order history.

fields.question: ❓Q: What payment methods are supported?
fields.answer: A: We support both Cash on Delivery and online card payments. Online payments simulate success or failure based on random outcomes for demo purposes.

fields.question: ❓Q: I forgot my password. What should I do?
fields.answer: A: Click on “Forgot Password” on the login page. A reset link will be sent to your registered email address.

fields.question: ❓Q: Can I update my address or profile info later?
fields.answer: A: Absolutely. Just head to the “Settings” page after logging in to update your name, address, phone number, or password.

fields.question: ❓Q: What happens if my online payment fails?
fields.answer: A: You’ll see a message with the reason for failure and an option to retry the payment. Don’t worry — your cart will stay intact.

fields.question: ❓Q: How do I leave a review for a product?
fields.answer: A: After purchasing, visit the product page while logged in and you’ll be able to submit a rating and comment.
